{"tid":1023010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【紐約華埠仇殺】中國男夜總會外遭射爆頭斃命 CCTV全程拍！","createTime":"2019-02-15T12:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T18:26:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"44797b4170b29f3fb07531984f04555c41ff16e5","tid":1023010,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T12:27:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190215/59262298\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190215%2F59262298&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qnpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=940e6fb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190215%2F59262298&h=f3a9c69c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190215/59262298</a><br />\n<br />\n【紐約華埠仇殺】中國男夜總會外遭射爆頭斃命 CCTV全程拍！<br />\n7小時前<br />\n即時兩岸<br />\n<br />\n美國紐約華埠法拉盛（Flushing）於當地時間12日凌晨2時35分左右發生槍擊案，一名來自中國的男子顧鑫（音譯：Xin Gu）在當地一間卡拉OK夜總會門外遭槍殺。當地警方指，槍手尾隨目標人物，並在其背後的頭部開了一槍，經初步調查懷疑是仇殺，暫時沒有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方提供的閉路電視所見，槍手戴上口罩和藍色手套。身穿大褸的顧男在夜總會門外抽煙踱步，不久有一輛Uber車接近，槍手立即從衫袋內取出手槍，在顧男背部開了一槍，擊中其頭部，待其倒地後再連開數槍。Uber司機立即駛離，槍手曾追趕一段距離。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n警方消息稱，死者為31歲中國男子顧鑫，案發時他在夜總會消遣後在門外遭一名蒙面槍手伏擊，頭部及身體連中5槍，被送院後證實傷重死亡。經了解，顧鑫為江蘇南通人，隨父母移民美國，先在法拉盛從事建築裝修生意，後來離開舊公司自立門戶，另開公司。<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約日報》<br />\n<br />\n10萬蚊 100人分！<br />\n星期一至五晚上10點半<br />\n《動腦Q》Let's Q the money！<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2QW8LcI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QW8LcI&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qnpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=472e8215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2QW8LcI</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190215/large/1550207179_c695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190215%2Flarge%2F1550207179_c695.jpg&h=3b74550b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n華裔男子遭槍手射爆頭慘死。(資料圖片)"},{"pid":"695a9b0dc8e997a97a22757eb7a4830299fd922c","tid":1023010,"uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T12:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OXwS2Kv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOXwS2Kv.gif&h=93b8161d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ede7135f91ce8d50adfce2b8126e3fcdf8071231","tid":1023010,"uid":99978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"695a9b0dc8e997a97a22757eb7a4830299fd922c","tid":1023010,"uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T12:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OXwS2Kv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOXwS2Kv.gif&h=93b8161d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T13:19:31.000Z","msg":"等你gif自癒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640bb4b0c8e159d6eb0e81c477b32288a36807e2","tid":1023010,"uid":221790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T13:24:18.000Z","msg":"Yoyo 福青幫第二把交椅"},{"pid":"dbbb2927ab23acff2d8c3228a864396abe31a758","tid":1023010,"uid":30569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T13:26:32.000Z","msg":"Gu xin gu xin~"},{"pid":"150add96ab296e4c371a1eef2153717ff72a5ac5","tid":1023010,"uid":26752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T13:27:12.000Z","msg":"希望佢來生再做中國人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"babcf50cffe57547269bb6c75d22646c881a3116","tid":1023010,"uid":209487,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T13:29:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9461d31944c30a4d126ae90e841b190e139fbbbe","tid":1023010,"uid":24282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T13:32:51.000Z","msg":"條片同無片有咩分別"},{"pid":"0b0a704cc952b9410f01c236def493593611c91f","tid":1023010,"uid":43003,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2